        <updateDate>2020-02-21T14:49:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Restore Everyone's Sleep Tonight Act of 2019 or the</b> <b>REST Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes an airport to impose an access restriction between the hours of 10 p.m. and 7 a.m. for aircrafts.</p> <p>An airport may impose a noise deterrence penalty on an air carrier or aircraft operator for a violation of the access restriction.</p> <p>The restriction does not apply to the operation of military, law enforcement, and Coast Guard flights.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
